@dclim your message has the same arguments as @gianm's and @jon-wei's, and still don't answer to my points:
- I DON'T suggest users to write custom extensions to enable the metric
- there are multiple issues with emitting query metrics by default, and the fact that it won't be emitted unless some other non-default configuration is set doesn't really void any of them.
